@startuml

[*] --> Register

Register : entry / New user
Register : do / Registration process
Register : exit / Successfully registered

Register --> Login : registration complete
Register --> [*] : invalid registration

Login : entry / Registered user
Login : do / Authenticate user
Login : exit / Access granted

Login --> Facilities : login successful
Login --> [*] : invalid login

Facilities : entry / User logged in
Facilities : do / Access available services
Facilities : exit / Selected service

Facilities --> Finance
Facilities --> HealthAZ
Facilities --> Resources
Facilities --> DrugsAndSupplements
Facilities --> NewsAndExperts
Facilities --> Payment
Facilities --> Feedback
Facilities --> Logout

Finance : entry / Insurance available
Finance : do / Purchase insurance or pay services
Finance : exit / Insurance validated
Finance --> Facilities

HealthAZ : entry / Select disease
HealthAZ : do / Display disease information
HealthAZ : exit / View result
HealthAZ --> Facilities

Resources : entry / Select resource
Resources : do / Access symptoms checker, calculator, doctor, ambulance
Resources : exit / View result
Resources --> Facilities

DrugsAndSupplements : entry / Doctor consulted
DrugsAndSupplements : do / Order medicines online
DrugsAndSupplements : exit / Medicine delivery initiated
DrugsAndSupplements --> Payment

Payment : entry / Service or medicine purchased
Payment : do / Process payment
Payment : exit / Payment completed
Payment --> Facilities

NewsAndExperts : entry / Choose news and experts
NewsAndExperts : do / Provide health awareness information
NewsAndExperts : exit / Information displayed
NewsAndExperts --> Facilities

Feedback : entry / User gives feedback
Feedback : do / Collect review
Feedback : exit / Feedback submitted
Feedback --> Facilities

Logout : entry / User opts to logout
Logout : do / End session
Logout : exit / User logged out
Logout --> [*]

@enduml